Class Presenter<V>

java.lang.Object
  com.mvp4g.client.presenter.Presenter<V>
Type Parameters:
V - Class type of the view injected into the presenter
All Implemented Interfaces:
PresenterInterface<V>
public class Presenter<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements PresenterInterface<V>

Default implementation of PresenterInterface.

This implementation has two attribute:

  • an event bus
  • a view
You should extend this class to create a presenter.
